title: Bünyamin Atay
text:
Hi all!
My name is Bünyamin Atay. I am a doctoral student at Counseling Psychology program in University of Wisconsin-Milwaukee. I am currently working with Dr. Autin. My research interests lie in psychological wellbeing, vocational development, measurement in counseling psychology. In this website, you can find all the avenues I am interested in.


Education
PhD in Counseling Psychology (ongoing)| University of Wisconsin-Milwaukee
PhD in Psychological Counseling (ongoing)| Middle East Technical University
MS in Psychological Counseling (2021)| Middle East Technical University
BA in Psychological Counseling (2018)| Hacettepe University


Experience
Graduate Assistant (2023 - Present)| University of Wisconsin-Milwaukee
Teaching/Research Assistant (2019-2023) | TED University
